No. 1474,

Misc.

Haynes v. United States. Charles Alan Wright for petitioner. Solicitor General Marshall, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, Beatrice Rosenberg and Kirby W. Patterson for the United States.

C. A. 5th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed m forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Case transferred to appellate docket and set for oral argument immediately following No. 181.
